      </div>

      <h2 class="exit-popup-title">Wait! Don't Leave Empty-Handed üéÅ</h2>

      <p class="exit-popup-subtitle">
        Get a <strong>FREE $997 Digital Marketing Audit</strong> before you go!
      </p>

      <ul class="exit-popup-benefits">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Comprehensive SEO Analysis</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Conversion Rate Review</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Competitor Research</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Growth Strategy Roadmap</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="exit-popup-ctas">
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/61487286451?text=Hi%2C%20I%20was%20about%20to%20leave%20but%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20the%20free%20%24997%20audit%21"
          class="exit-popup-btn exit-popup-btn-primary"
